msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are free of greed, hate, and delusion "
"for sights known by the eye, who are peaceful inside, and who conduct "
"themselves well by way of body, speech, and mind. They deserve honor, "
"respect, reverence, and veneration."

msgctxt "mn150:5.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

#. VAR: Mayampi hi → mayaṃ hi (?)
